Package main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EnemyModel
    The super class for all enemy types.
    Factory
    A utilization of the factory design pattern to generate gameplay objects such as turrets and enemies.
    GameModel
    Contains the logic of the game used to update information during the rounds.
    GameView
    Controls what happens when a button is clicked on the main menu and what is the next action that the needs to happen in the game.
    Main
    Starts the game by calling a new instance of the GameController.
    PathModel
    Controls the path of the enemies using a system of coordinate pairs on each of the paths corners.
    PlayerModel
    A container for the attributes of the game that are relevant and related to the player.
    Posn
    Keeps track of each pair of x and y coordinates that make up the positions that are the boundaries of the path model.
    TowerModel
    Houses the attributes for the Towers that are created.
    UnitModel
    Houses the attributes that both Towers and Enemies share in common such as the name, posn coordinates, gameDescriptions and the fact descriptions that makes this educational.
